---
description: C#/.NET standards for the VoxMesh control plane
globs:
  - "services/control-plane/**"
  - "**/*.cs"
---

- .NET 10 LTS, ASP.NET Core, nullable reference types enabled, warnings as errors.
- PostgreSQL is the source of truth; Redis only for ephemeral session state, locks, rate
  limiting, caching, presence — never authoritative data.
- EF Core for regular transactional operations; Dapper only where profiling shows a need.
- gRPC for internal low-latency communication; REST for external administration APIs.
- OIDC / OAuth 2.0 for identity; least-privilege scopes; tenant isolation in every query.
- Audit-relevant operations (tenants, users, roles, retention, credentials) must write audit
  records.
